<!-- begin Colour block -->
<div class="pullquote info">
     <h2 class"fake-h3">Key information</h2>
    <hr />
<ul>
<li><strong>Dates:</strong> 01 - 19 July 2024</li>
<li><strong>Duration: 3</strong>&nbsp;weeks</li>
<li>London campus based</li>
<li>7.5 ECTS available</li>
<li>Earlybird fee: &pound;3,595</li>
<li>Standard fee: &pound;3,895</li>
</ul>
  </div>
<!-- end Colour block -->
</div>
<!-- end Highlight box widget --><div class="row wysiwyg">

<h3>Do you offer any discounts?</h3>
<p>We do&nbsp;offer discounts for blockbookings for groups of students coming from the same university, refer a friend discounts and a discount of £300 if you attend both summer schools. For more information about discounts,&nbsp;<a href="/medicine/study/revolutions-in-biomedicine-summer-schools/ask-a-question/">ask us a question</a>&nbsp;and a member of the team will get back to you.&nbsp;</p>
<h3>How do I pay?</h3>
<p>The full course fee for the On Campus Summer School is <strong>£3,895</strong> per person. Payment must be made by credit or debit card through our online payment portal. We are unable to hold a place on the&nbsp;course before full payment is received. It is not possible for payment to be made in stages; payment must be received in full for your place to be confirmed.</p>
<h3>When do I pay the fee?</h3>
<p>It is important to make full payment promptly within 14 days of receiving your conditional offer to secure your place.</p>
<h3>Do you offer refunds for the fee?</h3>
<p>You are able to cancel your confirmed place within 14 days, after this time the&nbsp;course fee is not refundable.&nbsp;</p>
<h3>Do you offer scholarships?</h3>
<p>We offer&nbsp;a variety of scholarships&nbsp;based on academic potential for the Summer School. For further information please visit the&nbsp;<a href="/medicine/study/revolutions-in-biomedicine-summer-schools/scholarships/">scholarship information page.</a></p>
</div><div class="row wysiwyg">

<p><img class="full " alt="" src="/media/images/banner-bottom-block-3000x850/sus-footer-only-cropped-2_1643971578192-3000px.webp" /></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>
